---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Terms of Service | Apex Corporate Solutions'>
    <section class='py-20 bg-background'>
        <div class='container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-3xl'>
            <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8'>
                Terms of Service
            </h1>

            <div
                class='prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8'
            >
                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        1. Payment Terms
                    </h2>
                    <p class='text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed'>
                        All hosting and service fees are due on the 1st of every
                        month. Invoices will be sent via email 7 days prior to
                        the due date. Failure to make payment by the due date
                        may result in service interruption.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        2. Service Suspension
                    </h2>
                    <p class='text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed'>
                        Accounts that remain unpaid by the 4th of the month will
                        be automatically suspended. A reconnection fee of R150
                        may be charged to reactivate suspended accounts. We
                        reserve the right to terminate accounts that are
                        consistently in arrears.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        3. Cancellation Policy
                    </h2>
                    <p class='text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed'>
                        Services may be cancelled with one calendar month's
                        notice. Notice must be given in writing via email to
                        accounts@apexcorporate.co.za. No refunds will be issued
                        for partial months of service.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>
                        4. Acceptable Use
                    </h2>
                    <p class='text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed'>
                        Our hosting services may not be used for any illegal
                        activities, spamming, or hosting of malicious content.
                        We reserve the right to immediately terminate any
                        account found to be in violation of this policy without
                        refund.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-4'>5. Liability</h2>
                    <p class='text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed'>
                        While we strive for 99.9% uptime, Apex Corporate
                        Solutions shall not be held liable for any loss of
                        business or data resulting from service interruptions,
                        hardware failure, or force majeure events. Clients are
                        encouraged to maintain their own backups of critical
                        data.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
